General Assembly Joint Convention
Resolution No. 3
February Session, 2026 LCO No. 409
Referred to Committee on NO COMMITTEE
Introduced by:
SEN. DUFF, 25th Dist.
REP. ROJAS, 9th Dist.
RESOLUTION CONCERNING THE PRINTING OF THE GOVERNOR'S
BUDGET MESSAGE.
Resolved by this Assembly:
1 That the message of the Governor be printed in the journals of the
2 Senate and the House of Representatives and that a sufficient number
3 of copies be printed for general distribution.
